outputs.output_descr: Reduce extreme poverty and improving income generation and food security among vulnerable groups through community mobilization, agro-based micro-enterprises, skills training and post-training support; and b) promoting social inclusion in the service delivery system through the participation of out of school children; community awareness of maternal and child health; and capacity of service providers in planning and executing community-based water, sanitation and primary health/hygiene schemes.

project_descr: Community Mobilization for Poverty Alleviation and Social Inclusion in Service Delivery
